#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.77"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.77:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:0.2"
msgid "8. Ānandavagga "
msgstr "8. Ānanda "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.77:0.3"
msgid "77. Dutiyabhavasutta "
msgstr "77. Continued Existence (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.77:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:1.2"
msgid "“bhavo, bhavoti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘continued existence’. "

msgctxt "an3.77:1.3"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, bhavo hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How is continued existence defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.77:2.1"
msgid "“Kāmadhātuvepakkañca, ānanda, kammaṃ nābhavissa, api nu kho kāmabhavo paññāyethā”ti? "
msgstr "“If, Ānanda, there were no deeds to result in the sensual realm, would continued existence in the sensual realm still come about?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:2.2"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:2.3"
msgid "“Iti kho, ānanda, kammaṃ khettaṃ, viññāṇaṃ bījaṃ, taṇhā sneho. "
msgstr "“So, Ānanda, deeds are the field, consciousness is the seed, and craving is the moisture. "

msgctxt "an3.77:2.4"
msgid "Avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ hīnāya dhātuyā cetanā patiṭṭhitā patthanā patiṭṭhitā evaṃ āyatiṃ punabbhavābhinibbatti hoti. "
msgstr "The intention and aim of sentient beings—hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving—is established in a lower realm. That’s how there is rebirth into a new state of existence in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.77:3.1"
msgid "Rūpadhātuvepakkañca, ānanda, kammaṃ nābhavissa, api nu kho rūpabhavo paññāyethā”ti? "
msgstr "If there were no deeds to result in the realm of luminous form, would continued existence in the realm of luminous form still come about?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:3.2"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:3.3"
msgid "“Iti kho, ānanda, kammaṃ khettaṃ, viññāṇaṃ bījaṃ, taṇhā sneho. "
msgstr "“So, Ānanda, deeds are the field, consciousness is the seed, and craving is the moisture. "

msgctxt "an3.77:3.4"
msgid "Avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ majjhimāya dhātuyā cetanā patiṭṭhitā patthanā patiṭṭhitā evaṃ āyatiṃ punabbhavābhinibbatti hoti. "
msgstr "The intention and aim of sentient beings—hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving—is established in a middle realm. That’s how there is rebirth into a new state of existence in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an3.77:4.1"
msgid "Arūpadhātuvepakkañca, ānanda, kammaṃ nābhavissa, api nu kho arūpabhavo paññāyethā”ti? "
msgstr "If there were no deeds to result in the formless realm, would continued existence in the formless realm still come about?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:4.2"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.77:4.3"
msgid "“Iti kho, ānanda, kammaṃ khettaṃ, viññāṇaṃ bījaṃ, taṇhā sneho. "
msgstr "“So, deeds are the field, consciousness is the seed, and craving is the moisture. "

msgctxt "an3.77:4.4"
msgid "Avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ paṇītāya dhātuyā cetanā patiṭṭhitā patthanā patiṭṭhitā evaṃ āyatiṃ punabbhavābhinibbatti hoti. "
msgstr "The intention and aim of sentient beings—hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving—is established in a higher realm. That’s how there is rebirth into a new state of existence in the future. "

msgctxt "an3.77:4.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, ānanda, bhavo hotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how continued existence is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.77:4.6"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
